\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}3^n\sin\left(\frac 1 {4^nx}\right)
[1,\infty)
\forall\epsilon>0 
N\in\mathbb N
\forall n>N,p\in\mathbb N,x\in[1,\infty)
N
\left|\sum_{k=n+1}^{n+p}3^k\sin\left(\frac 1 {4^kx}\right)\right|<\epsilon.
|\sin y|\leq |y|
y\in\mathbb{R}
|x|\geq 1
N
\Big|\sum_{k=n+1}^{n+p}3^k\sin \left(\frac{1}{4^kx}\right)\Big|\leq \sum_{k=n+1}^{n+p}\left(\frac{3}{4}\right)^k=\frac{\left(\frac{3}{4}\right)^{n+1}-\left(\frac{3}{4}\right)^{n+p+1}}{1-\frac{3}{4}}\leq 4\left(\frac{3}{4}\right)^{n+1}
